<org.eclipse.epf.uma:ContentDescription xmi:version="2.0" xmlns:xmi="http://www.omg.org/XMI" xmlns:org.eclipse.epf.uma="http://www.eclipse.org/epf/uma/1.0.6/uma.ecore" xmi:id="-KruwyDnFg1HaLU8BO3jhvg" name="new_discipline,_5WmxwFHXEdy72tV0zV7--Q" guid="-KruwyDnFg1HaLU8BO3jhvg" authors=" J Boyer" changeDate="2011-09-21T19:50:00.671+0200" version="7.5.0" mainDescription="&lt;a id=&quot;XE_rule_governance&quot; name=&quot;XE_rule_governance&quot;>&lt;/a> &#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;MARGIN: 0in 0in 0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial&quot;>Developing or customizing the governance&#xD;&#xA;    processes is an incremental activity. As the processes are deployed across departments, there are always tension&#xD;&#xA;    between IT and Business teams. The idea is to start simple, and involve IT and Business stakeholders in the process&#xD;&#xA;    design. After first implementation it is possible to fine tune the processes.&lt;/span>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&lt;br style=&quot;MARGIN: 3pt 0cm&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; />&#xD;&#xA;&lt;br />&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;MARGIN: 3pt 0cm&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    The architect is one of the main roles responsible for designing the&amp;nbsp;governance processes.&amp;nbsp; He or she should&#xD;&#xA;    follow the steps below:&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 3pt 0cm 3pt 18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 18.0pt&quot;&#xD;&#xA;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span style=&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;mso-list: Ignore&quot;>·&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span> Develop the&#xD;&#xA;    organization map for all the departments involved in the rule approach.&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 3pt 0cm 3pt 18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 18.0pt&quot;&#xD;&#xA;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span style=&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;mso-list: Ignore&quot;>·&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span> Assign rule&#xD;&#xA;    set responsibility and access control&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 3pt 0cm 3pt 18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 18.0pt&quot;&#xD;&#xA;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span style=&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;mso-list: Ignore&quot;>·&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span> Define the&#xD;&#xA;    rule life cycle, rule set life cycle and domain object model changes&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 3pt 0cm 3pt 18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 18.0pt&quot;&#xD;&#xA;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span style=&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;mso-list: Ignore&quot;>·&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span> Develop each&#xD;&#xA;    major processes to support rule management on top of the BRMS&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 3pt 0cm 3pt 18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 18.0pt&quot;&#xD;&#xA;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span style=&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;mso-list: Ignore&quot;>·&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span> Document&#xD;&#xA;    those process to communicate to all stakeholders using BPMN or UML activity diagram&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;TEXT-INDENT: -18pt; MARGIN: 3pt 0cm 3pt 18pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list 18.0pt&quot;&#xD;&#xA;class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;span style=&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Symbol; mso-bidi-font-family: Symbol; mso-fareast-font-family: Symbol&quot;>&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;mso-list: Ignore&quot;>·&lt;span&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;FONT: 7pt 'Times New Roman'&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/span> Design and&#xD;&#xA;    build the tools to support those processes:&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;div style=&quot;MARGIN-TOP: 0cm; MARGIN-LEFT: 2em&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;ul style=&quot;MARGIN-TOP: 0cm&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li style=&quot;MARGIN: 3pt 0cm; mso-list: l1 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 72.0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;            Implement the rule extensions model to support those processes by adding meta data on top of the rule&#xD;&#xA;            artifacts. &lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes&quot;>&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span>&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;li style=&quot;MARGIN: 3pt 0cm; mso-list: l1 level2 lfo1; tab-stops: list 72.0pt&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;            &lt;span style=&quot;mso-ansi-language: EN&quot; lang=&quot;EN&quot;>customize the behavior of&amp;nbsp;the BRMS&amp;nbsp;by implementing the&#xD;&#xA;            controller interface, to trigger event on specific action like the changes on the rule life cycle.&lt;/span>&#xD;&#xA;        &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/ul>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/div>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p style=&quot;MARGIN: 3pt 0cm&quot; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    For the business rule development and maintenance these processes are:&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;ul style=&quot;MARGIN-TOP: 0cm&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;li&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA;     class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        Rule change management process&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;li&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA;     class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        Rule execution monitoring process&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;li&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA;     class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        Rule authoring process&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;li&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA;     class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        Rule execution process&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;li&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA;     class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        Rule deployment process&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;li&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA;     class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        Rule testing process&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;li&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA;     class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        Rule retirement process&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;li&#xD;&#xA;    style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA;     class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;>&#xD;&#xA;        And the last process is about how to improve the current governance processes.&#xD;&#xA;    &lt;/li>&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/ul>&lt;br&#xD;&#xA;style=&quot;MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list 36.0pt; mso-pagination: none; mso-layout-grid-align: none&quot;&#xD;&#xA; class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; />&#xD;&#xA;&lt;br />" longPresentationName="new_discipline,_5WmxwFHXEdy72tV0zV7--Q"/>
